name: ExecutionMetrics
desc: Timing information to isolate service performance from network delays.

items.name: received
items.desc: The UTC time the service receives the request.

items.name: completed
items.desc: The UTC time the service finishes processing this Invocation.

items.name: duration
items.desc: The time, in seconds, that elapses while the service processes this request. Provide millisecond precision, if possible.
